  { q: "Should I wait for regulation before starting an Airbnb in Barrie?", a: "No. Existing operators almost always get grandfathered or given a grace period when new STR bylaws pass. If you start now, you establish operating history, build reviews, and position yourself to comply easily when rules come. Waiting means competing with 503+ existing listings later and potentially facing a license cap. The window is open today." }
